00:26:51,569 --> 00:26:54,947
-You made it! Must have been a long trip.
-Nah, it was fine.

252
00:27:02,246 --> 00:27:03,831
How've you been, my dear son?

253
00:27:07,376 --> 00:27:09,712
Give me a hug, it's been a while.

254
00:27:19,430 --> 00:27:21,724
What a tear-jerking mother-son reunion.

255
00:27:22,892 --> 00:27:25,102
Hyang-bok, is this your office?

256
00:27:25,186 --> 00:27:27,605
Yes. Office is here,
and residence at the back.

257
00:27:29,732 --> 00:27:33,402
Hey, what's wrong
with your hair this time?

258
00:27:33,694 --> 00:27:36,655
